
portfolioProjects:
  - title: Luxury Outdoor Living Space with Pool, Patio & Outdoor Kitchen
    location: Wellesley, MA
    description: >
      This Wellesley backyard was transformed into a complete outdoor living
      space featuring bluestone walkways, a spacious natural stone patio,
      stacked stone retaining walls, raised planting beds, a custom outdoor
      kitchen, and a wood-burning fireplace. The finished landscape creates a
      welcoming place for relaxing, entertaining, and enjoying the outdoors
      throughout every season.
